name: COSMOS #88
description: COSMOS: A RENGA Collection, is a bespoke collection that continues to evolve the world of RENGA beyond the known galaxies. Each piece is individually hand drawn with care, attention to detail, and destined to become a Star alongside those that came before. The artistic disciplines of illustration, cartooning, and storytelling join in collaboration with the community, as each documented character enters the COSMOS, onchain, forever.
